    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市响应美国因美联储利率信号而上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街股市创下新高后，亚洲股市周四上涨，因美联储暗示尽管近期通胀有所上升，但今年仍将进行三次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派鲍威尔推动金价首次突破每盎司 2,200 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储维持今年三次降息的预期后，金价首次跃升至每盎司 2,200 美元以上，这表明美联储并未对近期通胀上升感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本今年最大规模的首次公开募股后，Trial Holdings 飙升 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trial-holdings-set-to-debut-after-japan-s-largest-ipo-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[折扣店连锁运营商 Trial Holdings Inc. 在东京上市首日股价飙升 40%，此前该公司首次公开募股筹集了 388.5 亿日元（合 2.58 亿美元）资金，为日本今年规模最大的一次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trial-holdings-set-to-debut-after-japan-s-largest-ipo-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
