      <title>澳大利亚煤矿工人寻求私人资本，银行却心存疑虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/australian-coal-miners-woo-private-capital-as-banks-get-leery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚煤炭生产商越来越多地涉足高息私人贷款，因为贷款机构希望取代因 ESG 担忧而犹豫不决的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/australian-coal-miners-woo-private-capital-as-banks-get-leery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
